{"data":[{"name":"85:1","price":"誓以有宫分的苍穹，","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡبُرُوجِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5910,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi dhāti al-burūji ","translations":["By the sky","containing","the constellations","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","dhāti","al-burūji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3450],[2,3450,4120],[3,4120,8325]]}},{"name":"85:2","price":"和所警告的日子，","arabic":"وَٱلۡيَوۡمِ ٱلۡمَوۡعُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5911,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-yawmi al-mawʿūdi ","translations":["And the Day","Promised","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-yawmi","al-mawʿūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,5245]]}},{"name":"85:3","price":"以及能证的和所证的日子，","arabic":"وَشَاهِدٖ وَمَشۡهُودٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5912,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"washāhidin wamashhūdin ","translations":["And (the) witness","and what is witnessed","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["washāhidin","wamashhūdin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,6705]]}},{"name":"85:4","price":"愿掘坑的人们，被弃绝，","arabic":"قُتِلَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡأُخۡدُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5913,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"qutila aṣḥābu al-ukh'dūdi ","translations":["Destroyed were","(the) companions","(of) the pit","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["qutila","aṣḥābu","al-ukh'dūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1610],[3,1610,5935]]}},{"name":"85:5","price":"那坑里有燃料点着的火，","arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡوَقُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5914,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"al-nāri dhāti al-waqūdi ","translations":["(Of) the fire","full","(of) the fuel","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["al-nāri","dhāti","al-waqūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2120],[2,2120,2760],[3,2760,6735]]}},{"name":"85:6","price":"当时，他们坐在坑边，","arabic":"إِذۡ هُمۡ عَلَيۡهَا قُعُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5915,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"idh hum ʿalayhā quʿūdun ","translations":["When","they","by it","(were) sitting","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","hum","ʿalayhā","quʿūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,780],[3,780,1790],[4,1790,5425]]}},{"name":"85:7","price":"他们见证自己对信士们的罪行，","arabic":"وَهُمۡ عَلَىٰ مَا يَفۡعَلُونَ بِٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ شُهُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5916,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wahum ʿalā mā yafʿalūna bil-mu'minīna shuhūdun ","translations":["And they","over","what","they were doing","to the believers","witnesses","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wahum","ʿalā","mā","yafʿalūna","bil-mu'minīna","shuhūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1330],[3,1330,1730],[4,1730,3040],[5,3040,4550],[6,4550,8555]]}},{"name":"85:8","price":"他们对于信士们，只责备他们信仰安拉——万能的，可颂的主，","arabic":"وَمَا نَقَمُواْ مِنۡهُمۡ إِلَّآ أَن يُؤۡمِنُواْ بِٱللَّهِ ٱلۡعَزِيزِ ٱلۡحَمِيدِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5917,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā naqamū min'hum illā an yu'minū bil-lahi al-ʿazīzi al-ḥamīdi ","translations":["And not","they resented","[of] them","except","that","they believed","in Allah","the All-Mighty","the Praiseworthy","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","naqamū","min'hum","illā","an","yu'minū","bil-lahi","al-ʿazīzi","al-ḥamīdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1450],[3,1450,2250],[4,2250,4480],[5,4480,4959],[6,4959,6739],[7,6739,7839],[8,7839,8919],[9,8919,12274]]}},{"name":"85:9","price":"天地的主权只是他的，安拉是见证万物的。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي لَهُۥ مُلۡكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۚ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ شَهِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5918,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī lahu mul'ku al-samāwāti wal-arḍi wal-lahu ʿalā kulli shayin shahīdun ","translations":["The One Who","for Him","(is) the dominion","(of) the heavens","and the earth","and Allah","on","every","thing","(is) a Witness","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","lahu","mul'ku","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍi","wal-lahu","ʿalā","kulli","shayin","shahīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,1590],[3,1590,2270],[4,2270,3760],[5,3760,5210],[6,5210,6260],[7,6260,6830],[8,6830,7480],[9,7480,9300],[10,9300,13455]]}},{"name":"85:10","price":"迫害信士和信女而不悔过的人们，必受火狱的刑罚，并受火灾的惩治。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ فَتَنُواْ ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنَٰتِ ثُمَّ لَمۡ يَتُوبُواْ فَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ جَهَنَّمَ وَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ ٱلۡحَرِيقِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5919,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna fatanū al-mu'minīna wal-mu'mināti thumma lam yatūbū falahum ʿadhābu jahannama walahum ʿadhābu al-ḥarīqi ","translations":["Indeed","those who","persecuted","the believing men","and the believing women","then","not","they repented","then for them","(is the) punishment","(of) Hell","and for them","(is the) punishment","(of) the Burning Fire","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","fatanū","al-mu'minīna","wal-mu'mināti","thumma","lam","yatūbū","falahum","ʿadhābu","jahannama","walahum","ʿadhābu","al-ḥarīqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,2350],[3,2350,2980],[4,2980,4470],[5,4470,6070],[6,6070,7570],[7,7570,7890],[8,7890,8910],[9,8910,9710],[10,9710,10590],[11,10590,12330],[12,12330,13080],[13,13080,13970],[14,13970,17965]]}},{"name":"85:11","price":"信道而且行善的人们，必入下临诸河的乐园，那确是伟大的成功。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ جَنَّٰتٞ تَجۡرِي مِن تَحۡتِهَا ٱلۡأَنۡهَٰرُۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡفَوۡزُ ٱلۡكَبِيرُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5920,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna āmanū waʿamilū al-ṣāliḥāti lahum jannātun tajrī min taḥtihā al-anhāru dhālika al-fawzu al-kabīru ","translations":["Indeed","those who","believe","and do","the righteous deeds","for them","(will be) Gardens","flow","from","underneath it","the rivers","That","(is) the success","the great","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","āmanū","waʿamilū","al-ṣāliḥāti","lahum","jannātun","tajrī","min","taḥtihā","al-anhāru","dhālika","al-fawzu","al-kabīru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1600],[2,1600,2640],[3,2640,3830],[4,3830,4530],[5,4530,6020],[6,6020,6590],[7,6590,9359],[8,9359,10229],[9,10229,10859],[10,10859,12079],[11,12079,16139],[12,16139,16969],[13,16969,17799],[14,17799,21594]]}},{"name":"85:12","price":"你的主的惩治，确是严厉的。","arabic":"إِنَّ بَطۡشَ رَبِّكَ لَشَدِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5921,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna baṭsha rabbika lashadīdun ","translations":["Indeed","(the) Grip","(of) your Lord","(is) surely strong","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","baṭsha","rabbika","lashadīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2180],[3,2180,2950],[4,2950,6495]]}},{"name":"85:13","price":"他确能创造，且能再造，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ يُبۡدِئُ وَيُعِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5922,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu huwa yub'di-u wayuʿīdu ","translations":["Indeed He","He","originates","and repeats","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","huwa","yub'di-u","wayuʿīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2170],[2,2170,2500],[3,2500,3470],[4,3470,7205]]}},{"name":"85:14","price":"他是至赦的，是至爱的，","arabic":"وَهُوَ ٱلۡغَفُورُ ٱلۡوَدُودُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5923,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa al-ghafūru al-wadūdu ","translations":["And He","(is) the Oft-Forgiving","the Most Loving","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","al-ghafūru","al-wadūdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,510],[2,510,1310],[3,1310,5395]]}},{"name":"85:15","price":"是宝座的主，是尊严的，","arabic":"ذُو ٱلۡعَرۡشِ ٱلۡمَجِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5924,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"dhū al-ʿarshi al-majīdu ","translations":["Owner (of)","the Throne","the Glorious","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["dhū","al-ʿarshi","al-majīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,230],[2,230,1120],[3,1120,4665]]}},{"name":"85:16","price":"是为所欲为的。","arabic":"فَعَّالٞ لِّمَا يُرِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5925,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"faʿʿālun limā yurīdu ","translations":["Doer","of what","He intends","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["faʿʿālun","limā","yurīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1820],[3,1820,4835]]}},{"name":"85:17","price":"你曾听见军队的故事了吗？","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡجُنُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5926,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-junūdi ","translations":["Has","come to you","(the) story","(of) the hosts","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-junūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1220],[3,1220,2060],[4,2060,5365]]}},{"name":"85:18","price":"法老和赛莫德人的故事。","arabic":"فِرۡعَوۡنَ وَثَمُودَ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5927,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fir'ʿawna wathamūda ","translations":["Firaun","and Thamud","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["fir'ʿawna","wathamūda",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,4695]]}},{"name":"85:19","price":"不然，不信道的人们陷于否认之中，","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ فِي تَكۡذِيبٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5928,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"bali alladhīna kafarū fī takdhībin ","translations":["Nay","Those who","disbelieve","(are) in","denial","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["bali","alladhīna","kafarū","fī","takdhībin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,340],[2,340,1310],[3,1310,2200],[4,2200,2590],[5,2590,5945]]}},{"name":"85:20","price":"安拉是从各方面包罗他们的，","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ مِن وَرَآئِهِم مُّحِيطُۢ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5929,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-lahu min warāihim muḥīṭun ","translations":["But Allah","from","behind them","encompasses","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-lahu","min","warāihim","muḥīṭun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,2070],[3,2070,5530],[4,5530,8375]]}},{"name":"85:21","price":"不然，这是尊严的《古兰经》，","arabic":"بَلۡ هُوَ قُرۡءَانٞ مَّجِيدٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5930,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"bal huwa qur'ānun majīdun ","translations":["Nay","It","(is) a Quran","Glorious","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","huwa","qur'ānun","majīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,870],[3,870,1780],[4,1780,6085]]}},{"name":"85:22","price":"记录在一块受保护的天牌上。","arabic":"فِي لَوۡحٖ مَّحۡفُوظِۭ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5931,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fī lawḥin maḥfūẓin ","translations":["In","a Tablet","Guarded","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","lawḥin","maḥfūẓin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,1190],[3,1190,6315]]}}],"chapter":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj","Chapter Al-Buruj","Buruj","Surah Buruj","Chapter Buruj","Al Buruj","Surah Al Buruj","Chapter Al Buruj","Surah 85","Chapter 85","The Constellations","البروج"],"version":{"key":"chinese_makin","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"zh","version":"1.0.2","la